{"tid":199211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「無圖」舖頭停業　市民蜂擁搶貨","createTime":"2017-04-13T04:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T03:32:59.000Z","uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"986916019ff77c55dbc92b82aa83ae7d4aac45aa","tid":199211,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"出處：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170412/bkn-20170412145132691-0412_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170412%2Fbkn-20170412145132691-0412_00822_001.html&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6918fdb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170412/bkn-20170412145132691-0412_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1O2SQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1O2SQ0.jpg&h=ffdbcbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/13/124321_d423d13b4fa2fe5923d7687a0d35b01c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F124321_d423d13b4fa2fe5923d7687a0d35b01c.jpg&h=c027b651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食環清發霉生果揭舖頭停業　市民蜂擁搶貨<br />\n<br />\n荃灣路德圍一間開業30年的生果店停業10日，而店外所放滿的生果已經發霉，引起食環署關注，今早到場清走發霉生果才發現店主失蹤，而路經的市民得悉後，不消半小時便將店舖的生果取走。<br />\n<br />\n食環署今早到上址進行清場行動，將所有發霉的生果清走，而其他生果則放回原位。期間有市民透露店主已欠租多時並已失蹤，其他市民得悉後便蜂擁而至，店內的西瓜、士多啤梨、蘋果等生果不消半小時已被清光。<br />\n<br />\n當區區議員葛兆源透露，該生果店為區內龍頭，而且歷史悠久，幾日前食環署發現該店有發霉生果而出現衞生問題，需要前往清場，而期間他未能聯絡到店主及其家人，亦有街坊透露店主的財政狀況出現問題。他續指，該生果店大約有6至7名員工遭拖欠薪金，其中一位員工服務長達15年，單是該名員工保守估計已被拖欠薪金逾10萬港元，目前工會正聯絡其他員工以便提供協助。"},{"pid":"95b96c755d6d5566f15e422af324eef22e91c7e0","tid":199211,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"荃灣咁多支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4d24de3a5d1d95dbb356985005eded155ac8a1","tid":199211,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"店主應該有咁上下年紀<br />\n<br />\n咁樣失踪，多數....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地拎左生果還得到比店主先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ee0a88720b06bae576f982b0e51c09f7ced835","tid":199211,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"班老中坑最叻就係餓狗搶屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aecd2b1a18c13262a0d0b6bb5e9c1c29b6702e1","tid":199211,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"支那人真恐怖！"},{"pid":"b0ddec5441979ff97d629233230cb7c11fb347cf","tid":199211,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa57664cdec56170748c7ba791aacb0db4580fe2","tid":199211,"uid":28256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"好想佢地食到中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60db362d52f11ae7b76880cdfba74b93f322c205","tid":199211,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"難分支那定港豬<br />\n其實有冇分別?"},{"pid":"d349de635a743d42c1ec07ad4527226c11f88a75","tid":199211,"uid":20285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"與偉大祖國接軌"},{"pid":"45e883e44ffb0bc9b2733794b54563183f40b891","tid":199211,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"環保呀"},{"pid":"a893717b88fe311af2e13dff1e670a0d2b5e6675","tid":199211,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"向祖國接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd70cfcff9a770f1698c2053419a0f041615d070","tid":199211,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy