1e7ce05124b5","tid":199211,"uid":92166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"有時死撐係冇撚有用<br />\n<br />\n考慮環境衛生，公權力都只能夠清走發霉既，冇發霉既非無主之物，阿公都唔清得，係得蝗至會去&ldquo;救&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n唔好講到小學咁高層次，我個仔讀幼稚園，已經教唔係自己既野，唔好拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905dfb00a448006c31c4e5e0cc427a4d88f52957","tid":199211,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T08:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時死撐係冇撚有用<br />\n<br />\n考慮環境衛生，公權力都只能夠清走發霉既，冇發霉既非無主之物，阿公都唔清得，係得蝗至會去&ldquo;救&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n唔好講到小學咁高層次，我個仔讀幼稚園，已經教唔係自己既野，唔好拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係自己既野，唔好拎 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n好啱！但支拿人種永遠會搵借口比自己！"},{"pid":"263904cb4162cd7dea91a220ed798084d426fdb4","tid":199211,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f409cc4bd571e3fe740af3792cbf0dc0706beaa4","tid":199211,"uid":6280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"荃灣好撚多新香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1640935d2e1433056aef54ac1ac089bf2940cc53","tid":199211,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"香港人咪又係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0785be86981c78a442d5aa34252fbccde68abd79","tid":199211,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"無眼睇"},{"pid":"a91ba2bbe21a93384dcc9899af815965049a043c","tid":199211,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"應該死左？"},{"pid":"8a3740c8f9b9545be355809356fae22b146a7b23","tid":199211,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T12:44:23.000Z